c: 6
v: 112
t: "Nabiyow ama koros kok naqboytit kah abnennah Ambiyak kulli Nabiik seehadâ sheytoonaa kee jinni sheytoona naqboytit keenik abne, keenik mariiy marah deedal maxcoocay bilqiseeni ittal Qidan waswasah tet yaabbe mari edde duquurutankeh, Nabiyow ku- Rabbi faxinnay usun woh abak manannon, toysa usun diraabak ginnaasitaanam kee ken ittah cab"